

fea_si_ble

feasible = 可行的 / 做得到的

句型： a/an + feasible + 名詞
We need to find a feasible solution to this problem. (我們需要為這個問題找到一個可行的解決方案。)

A. 描述主詞 (主詞 + be + feasible)
The project is feasible if we have enough time. (如果我們有足夠的時間，這個專案是可行的。)

B. 描述受詞 (find + 受詞 + feasible)
The manager finds the new schedule feasible. (經理覺得新的時程表是可行的。)








The plan is feasible. (這個計畫是可行的。)
Working in Singapore is feasible for me. (去新加坡工作對我來說是可行的。)
It is feasible to finish the project by Friday.


1. 方案與計畫 (最常見)
The plan is feasible. (計畫可行。)
The proposal is feasible. (提案可行。)
This approach is feasible. (這個方法行得通。)

2. 目標與時間
The goal is feasible. (目標是可以達成的。)
The deadline is feasible. (截止日期是合理的/趕得上的。)
This target is feasible. (這個目標做得到。)

3. 具體措施
The solution is feasible. (這個解決方案可行。)
The option is feasible. (這個選項是可行的。)
The change is feasible. (這項變動是可行的。)


I have a feasible plan.
I have a feasible idea.
I have a feasible solution.


This plan is feasible.
Is it feasible to finish today?
The idea sounds good, but it is not feasible.
It is not feasible without more time.

We need a feasible solution.
